message: To get a high score, focus on creating a 'three-ingredient' item. Start by using the 'stove' to cook 'raw bacon' or 'raw fish' (protein) for 20 points. Then, combine this 'cooked protein' with a 'grain' item (like tortilla, wheat, or bread) for 40 points. Finally, add a 'vegetable' (like lettuce, tomato, cucumber, or carrot) to reach 60 points. message: Cook all raw proteins and vegetables with the 'stove' (they usually become value 20). Grains often stay at 0 value even when cooked.
